# Voice Assistant UI — Architecture & Design Specification

Production-ready interface for the desktop Voice Assistant. The **Liquid Blob** from `Liquid_Blob.html` is preserved as the primary visual identity and extended with a four-state assistant model, face-verification overlay, and Python backend bridge.

---

## 1. UI Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Viewport (100vw × 100vh, single immersive screen)          │
│  ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │
│  │ Layer 0: Background canvas (particles, gradients)     │  │
│  │ Layer 2: Blob stage (liquid blob canvas + light rays) │  │
│  │ Layer 4: HUD (status, clock, user badge)              │  │
│  │ Layer 5: Noise texture overlay                        │  │
│  │ Layer 6: Vignette                                     │  │
│  │ Layer 8: Camera overlay (conditional, right panel)    │  │
│  └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
         ▲                              ▲
         │ WebSocket / window.AssistantUI │
         └────────── ui/server.py ────────┘
                    clone_main.py
```

**Separation of concerns**

| Layer | Responsibility |
|-------|----------------|
| HTML | Semantic structure, ARIA, layer stacking |
| CSS tokens | Color, type, motion, spacing |
| CSS layout | Blob positioning, face-shift, responsive |
| CSS components | Status HUD, camera glass panel |
| `state-machine.js` | Single source of truth for assistant state |
| `liquid-blob.js` | Canvas rendering (preserved blob math) |
| `audio-analyzer.js` | FFT, RMS, frequency bands |
| `assistant-bridge.js` | Backend ↔ UI protocol |
| `camera-overlay.js` | Face verification UI |

---

## 2. Layout Specification

| Element | Position | Size |
|---------|----------|------|
| Blob stage | Center (shifts left `-14vw` when face active) | `min(72vmin, 720px)` square |
| Status block | Below blob, centered | Fluid typography |
| Clock | Top-right fixed | Label size |
| User badge | Top-left fixed | Label size |
| Camera panel | Right center (mobile: bottom) | `min(28vw, 420px)` |

**Breathing space:** `clamp(2rem, 8vh, 6rem)` minimum margin around blob. No sidebars, menus, or dashboards.

---

## 3. Component Hierarchy

```
App
├── BackgroundLayer (#bgCanvas)
├── BlobStage
│   ├── LightRays
│   └── LiquidBlob (#blobCanvas)
├── NoiseOverlay
├── Vignette
├── Clock
├── UserBadge
├── StatusDisplay
│   ├── status-primary
│   ├── status-secondary
│   └── indicators (mic, camera)
└── CameraOverlay
    ├── video.camera-feed
    ├── canvas (face box / landmarks)
    └── meta (status, user, confidence bar)
```

---

## 4. Motion Design Specification

| Transition | Properties | Duration | Easing |
|------------|------------|----------|--------|
| State label change | opacity, translateY | 300ms | `ease-out-soft` |
| Blob stage scale (listening) | transform scale | 500ms | `cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1)` |
| Blob horizontal shift (face) | transform translateX | 700ms | `ease-out-soft` |
| Camera panel enter/exit | opacity, translateX/Y | 500–700ms | `ease-out-soft` |
| Glow / bloom | shadow, gradient stops | 500ms | fluid |
| Internal blob morph | radius smoothing | per-frame 0.1 factor | exponential smooth |

**Principles:** Physics-inspired, organic, purpose-driven. No decorative random motion.

---

## 5. Animation State Machine

```
                    ┌──────────┐
         ┌─────────│ DORMANT  │◄────────────────┐
         │         └────┬─────┘                 │
         │              │ wake / mic active      │ idle / done
         │              ▼                        │
         │         ┌──────────┐                 │
         │         │LISTENING │                 │
         │         └────┬─────┘                 │
         │              │ speech end            │
         │              ▼                        │
         │         ┌──────────┐                 │
         │         │ THINKING │                 │
         │         └────┬─────┘                 │
         │              │ TTS start             │
         │              ▼                        │
         │         ┌──────────┐    audio end     │
         └────────►│ SPEAKING │─────────────────┘
                   └──────────┘

Parallel overlay: FACE_VERIFICATION
  - Blob shifts left, camera panel slides in
  - On complete: panel fades, blob recenters
```

**Blend index** (0–3) smooths visually between states for the blob renderer.

---

## 6. Color System

Defined in `css/tokens.css`:

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--color-white` | `#f5fbff` | Highlights |
| `--color-ice` | `#a0d2ff` | Secondary text |
| `--color-cyan` | `#48d8e8` | Listening accent |
| `--color-navy` | `#0a1628` | Deep surfaces |
| `--color-black` | `#030405` | Background base |
| `--color-glass-bg` | `rgba(8,18,32,0.45)` | Camera panel |
| `--color-success` | green-cyan | Verified |
| `--color-warning` | warm amber | Unknown face |

No saturated rainbow. Accent colors only for semantic status.

---

## 7. Typography System

- **Family:** Inter 200/300/400 (system fallback)
- **Status:** `clamp(1.1rem, 2.2vw, 1.75rem)`, weight 200, letter-spacing 0.12em
- **Labels:** uppercase, `0.28em` tracking, muted ice blue
- **Clock:** thin, top-right, minimal presence

---

## 8. Camera Overlay Design

- **Glassmorphism:** `backdrop-filter: blur(18px)`, semi-transparent navy fill
- **Border:** 1px gradient stroke (ice blue → transparent)
- **Shadow:** deep drop + soft cyan glow
- **Content:** mirrored live video, rounded 24px corners
- **Overlays:** face bounding box (cyan stroke + glow), optional landmark dots
- **Meta:** status line, user name, confidence % + thin progress bar

**Statuses:** Scanning…, Recognizing, Liveness Check, Verified, Unknown Face, Error

---

## 9. Blob Interaction Behavior

Preserved from `Liquid_Blob.html`:

| State | Blob behavior |
|-------|---------------|
| Dormant | Slow noise morph, soft radial gradient, minimal glow |
| Listening | +6% scale, wave rings, orbiting particles, wave lines |
| Thinking | Slow internal flow noise, rotating highlight orbits, gentle pulse |
| Speaking | Multi-octave spikes driven by low/mid/high/RMS bands |

Audio analysis: 512-point FFT, band splits at bins 8/40/128, RMS from time domain.

---

## 10. Assistant State Transitions

Controlled via:

1. `stateMachine.setState('listening')` (JS)
2. `window.AssistantUI.setState('thinking')` (injected)
3. WebSocket `{ "type": "state", "value": "speaking" }`
4. Python `UIBridge.set_state('speaking')`

CSS `data-state` on `.app` drives stage glow and scale. Blob blend interpolates over ~300–700ms.

---

## 11. Responsive Behavior

| Breakpoint | Behavior |
|------------|----------|
| 1920×1080 | Default proportions |
| 1440p | Same vmin scaling |
| 4K (2560+) | Larger blob cap (900px), narrower camera panel ratio |
| ≤900px | Face mode: blob shifts up, camera panel bottom-centered |
| Resizable | Canvas DPR capped at 2, blob uses vmin |

---

## 12. CSS Architecture

```
ui/css/
  tokens.css      — design tokens only
  base.css        — reset, accessibility
  layout.css      — app shell, blob stage, layers
  components/
    status.css    — HUD, indicators, clock, user
    camera-panel.css — overlay panel
```

BEM-like naming: `.camera-overlay`, `.status-primary`, `.indicator--mic`.

---

## 13. JavaScript Architecture

```
ui/js/
  main.js                 — bootstrap
  core/
    event-bus.js          — pub/sub
    state-machine.js      — assistant FSM
    easing.js             — lerp, smooth
  audio/
    audio-analyzer.js     — FFT / RMS
  blob/
    liquid-blob.js        — canvas renderer
  components/
    background.js
    status-display.js
    camera-overlay.js
  bridge/
    assistant-bridge.js   — WebSocket + window API
```

ES modules, `requestAnimationFrame` render loops, no framework dependency.

---

## 14. Accessibility

- `role="application"` on root with `aria-label`
- Status text `aria-live="polite"` for screen reader announcements
- `prefers-reduced-motion` disables CSS transitions
- Camera overlay `aria-label="Face verification"`
- Confidence bar `role="progressbar"`
- State communicated visually first; text is secondary reinforcement

---

## 15. Performance Recommendations

1. Cap `devicePixelRatio` at 2 on blob and background canvases
2. Background particles: 60 (viewport) + 120 (blob) — reduce on low-end via `?quality=low`
3. Single RAF loop per canvas; avoid layout thrashing
4. WebSocket audio: batch PCM chunks ≥512 samples
5. Use `will-change: transform` sparingly on blob stage only during face transition
6. Preconnect Google Fonts; self-host for offline production

